{"tw": {"2262220": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "閃耀之石：英雄覺醒", "steam_appid": 2262220, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [2513400], "detailed_description": "<strong>《閃耀之石：英雄覺醒》</strong> 是一部成人視覺小說，圍繞浪漫、友誼、超能力和超級英雄等主題，故事發生在一個由強大的巨頭企業主導的反烏託邦世界，貪婪和腐敗猖獗。善良幾乎蕩然無存。<br>你能發現自己的力量嗎？而且……這會是你的真正力量嗎？！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/e66efa4af088679077e5a71c098fa3e8.poster.avif?t=1766344874\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/e66efa4af088679077e5a71c098fa3e8.webm?t=1766344874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/e66efa4af088679077e5a71c098fa3e8.mp4?t=1766344874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>這是一款以故事爲主導的遊戲，你將沉浸於一個完整的故事之中。<br>遊戲中，你將做出諸多選擇，這些選擇將影響你與其他角色的關係，以及你體驗冒險的方式。愛情、友情、浪漫、希望和恐懼都將伴隨你踏上這段旅程。你將以 Lambda 公司員工的身份開始，但很快，你就會發現自己擁有別人所沒有的東西……而這將永遠改變你的人生。<br><br>來吧，跟隨你已故父親的格言，在這個金錢和腐敗充斥的世界裡，嘗試運用你新獲得的力量行善！<br>來吧，你會發現，你新獲得的力量或許並非那些神所說的真正力量！<br>來吧，覺醒吧，成爲真正的超級英雄！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/0ad35e8093afbc5af6493b521b48ff1a.poster.avif?t=1766344874\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/0ad35e8093afbc5af6493b521b48ff1a.webm?t=1766344874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/0ad35e8093afbc5af6493b521b48ff1a.mp4?t=1766344874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>你將邂逅六位美麗迷人的女性，並與之共度浪漫時光。她們每個人都擁有獨特的個性、風格和故事。你會與她們所有人共度浪漫時光，還是只選擇與其中一位相守？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/10fcf3c674cdeeae4229e60dcee6be3b.poster.avif?t=1766344874\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/10fcf3c674cdeeae4229e60dcee6be3b.webm?t=1766344874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/10fcf3c674cdeeae4229e60dcee6be3b.mp4?t=1766344874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>如果沒有一些火爆、色情的淫穢場景供您體驗和享受，成人故事又會是什麼樣子呢？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/35cb585cf3ade86074a7e753b82bdddc.poster.avif?t=1766344874\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/35cb585cf3ade86074a7e753b82bdddc.webm?t=1766344874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/35cb585cf3ade86074a7e753b82bdddc.mp4?t=1766344874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>爲了生存下去並成爲真正的英雄，你需要朋友！<br><br>你可以依靠像你最好的朋友格雷格這樣的人，以及他美麗的妻子希拉，以及許多其他角色，他們會在你不可思議的旅程中幫助你！讓你體驗他們的故事……有的悲傷，有的善良，還有的……相當色情。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/eb898660ed50670044681a63edc3da36.poster.avif?t=1766344874\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/eb898660ed50670044681a63edc3da36.webm?t=1766344874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/eb898660ed50670044681a63edc3da36.mp4?t=1766344874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>英雄的真正價值取決於他敵人的實力！在這款遊戲中，你會遇到並發現許多這樣的英雄！<br><br>當然，想要贏得這些戰鬥絕非易事！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/9218a657d2a5c76084824f8712be67d0.poster.avif?t=1766344874\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/9218a657d2a5c76084824f8712be67d0.webm?t=1766344874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/9218a657d2a5c76084824f8712be67d0.mp4?t=1766344874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>故事中的世界介於我們自己的世界和當代賽博朋克世界之間。<br><br>在這個世界裡，現存的巨型企業比各國政府更強大，並且傾向於制定政策和法律。<br><br>故事發生的城鎮「月亮城」是一個融合了光明奇妙的城市和黑暗粗獷的特大都市的城鎮。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/2f84ed2a960f0138c72bba48fb5450ff.poster.avif?t=1766344874\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/2f84ed2a960f0138c72bba48fb5450ff.webm?t=1766344874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/2f84ed2a960f0138c72bba48fb5450ff.mp4?t=1766344874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>在這個世界上，你會遇到其他「人」，其中一些可能更加強大，他們俯視着你和你的故事。但在你的旅程中，他們會是你的盟友還是敵人？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/515075db241906427c7cda12fd0c9416.poster.avif?t=1766344874\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262220/extras/515075db241906427c7cda12fd0c9416.webm?t=1766344874\" ty